                            <comment id="13000170" author="mielket" created="Tue, 9 Sep 2014 04:39:20 -0400"  >&lt;p&gt;I tested the jpa20 backport of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ARIES-885&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;ARIES-885&lt;/a&gt; today using different databases (MySQL, Microsoft SQL Server 2008) and drivers (jtds, Microsoft&apos;s sqljdbc4.jar and MySQL driver) and found the problem fixed.&lt;br/&gt;
